<br>
there are good divisions between newbie and lowbie areas, and it would be possible to level from 1-30 there if you really wanted to and you'd still come out rich (mabey even higher I don't know how tough ice giants are). Combine that with Halas, Blackburrow and Permafrost and you've got a mini EQ domain all in 4 zones.<br>
